==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ordinarily
<hw>Or"di*na*ri*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>According to
established rules or settled method; as a rule; commonly; usually; in
most cases; <as>as, a winter more than <ex>ordinarily</ex>
severe</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Those who <qex>ordinarily</qex> pride themselves not a little upon
their penetration.</q> <rj><qau>I. Taylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ordinary</ent>⟦br⟧
